Company Overview of Ferox Capital Management LLP



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Ferox Capital Management LLP is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm launches and manages hedge funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm employs bottom-up and top-down analysis to make its investments. It primarily invests in convertible bonds to make its investments. Ferox Capital Management LLP was founded in 2000, and is based in London, United Kingdom.


